description: To contribute to OBJKT4OBJKT I wanted to include something personal. This was made during a low point in quarantine as a response to the US's treatment of workers. In America, we idolize workaholism. Basic rights like a living wage and healthcare are considered privileges. Unless you're a millionaire you survive on a razors edge. And our leaders don't care, so it can be hopeless. But creating art in a digital medium has really helped me cope and explore those feelings.
